song.title: Variform (Takomo Remix)
song.info: Remixed and reproduced by Otto Hassinen and Pekka Kokkonen in 2004-2005. Inspiration provided by The Autobots, Chris Carter, Distortionz, DJ Mutiny, Koma & Bones, Ed Rush & Optical, Matrix and Cause 4 Concern. Shoutouts to Matt Current, Mfx, Kewlers, LBJ, Rel1, Hoffman, Influenza, Cereal Killaz, Hot Flush Recordings, Silo Recordings, Bassreflex crew and everyone else who's been supporting us. ..
